Workshops on networking etiquette are held in an adjoining classroom, where students rehearse their elevator pitches while clutching resumes in branded folders. Career counselors guide students on maintaining eye contact during presentations and assist international students seeking advice on visa sponsorship. As the fair nears its conclusion, announcement chimes signal the end of the event, event staff scan registrations and distribute lanyards, while friends gather on the quad to decompress and share experiences. QR codes for immediate internship applications attract interest as well.

Inside, students introduce themselves, with some quietly rehearsing elevator pitches against the wall. A data science company showcases a live dashboard of fair attendance, and healthcare providers display community outreach photos. Consulting firms provide glossy case study booklets on high tables, while a cybersecurity company runs a password cracking challenge on a laptop. Finance firms offer QR codes for immediate internship applications, and career counselors redirect unsure students toward applicable industries, reminding attendees to maintain eye contact during their presentations. An alumni panel discusses preparation for technical interviews, and workshops on networking etiquette are held in an adjoining classroom. A whiteboard prominently displays a list of employers scheduling same-day interviews.
